<br>
Normaly, if I want a complex background, I would draw it at the same time I draw my character (all on one sheet) or I could draw the character first and after I would draw the background (both on different sheets, and merge them after with photoshop).<br>
<br>
If the background I want is nothing special (like boring lines), I would color the character first. Next, I would go in Illustrator to draw the lines. Finally, I would bring back the lines in photoshop to change them a little.<br>
<br>
